<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.9.3">
<l>paṟaiyumviṉai toḻutuymmiṉīr paṇiyumciṟu toṇṭīr.</l>
<l>aṟaiyumpuṉa lorupālvaya lorupālpoḻi lorupāl</l>
<l>ciṟaivaṇṭiṉa maṟaiyuñciṟu puliyūrccala cayaṉat</l>
<l>tuṟaiyumiṟai yaṭiyallatoṉ ṟiṟaiyumaṟi yēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Karma will vanish; you who are low, inferior servants, adoring [him], be saved.</l>
<l>I do not know a scintilla of anything but the feet of the god</l>
<l>Who dwells on a watery bed in Ciṟupuliyūr</l>
<l rend="indent">where hum swarms of winged bees,</l>
<l>With groves on one side, fields on one side, and crashing waves on one side.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
